{"tid":372661,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[有腥post]  燒鯖魚","createTime":"2017-08-24T12:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T16:53:20.000Z","uid":123204,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"953274c44b2d3b20499f3cb901af0e945437dab8","tid":372661,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"話說前日腥親大家 今晚都係整魚 所以寫明係標題到有腥 慎入<br />\n<br />\n講返燒鯖魚<br />\n黎味菜同殺你啊雞翼一樣都係易過借火 多小小功夫咁解<br />\n個人認為最啱女友上黎時整佢食 <br />\n好過煎扒 熟又話un 生又話有血水唔食得好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋清清地加碗白飯就食完 大家唔洗太飽 留力食下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料好簡單<br />\n鯖魚<br />\n鹽<br />\n<br />\n百佳藍色一pack 有時做promote 20蚊4包最平+最難食<br />\n惠康好似有兩隻一平一貴<br />\n27蚊兩塊/27蚊2包2塊<br />\n凍肉鋪就十蚊到 個人最愛<br />\n<br />\n今日太遲走就揀咗惠康 27蚊2包2塊整<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ukf4z9vp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fukf4z9vp&h=0aaaca9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一件事就成包掉落水解凍"},{"pid":"fef62b99971320f83c5cd10ba0c11cb535a18ca5","tid":372661,"uid":29464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:57:59.000Z","msg":"十卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全屋得我一個鍾意食鯖魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好少有機會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9f6061157c751eb8a58161dc795ce463e62b88","tid":372661,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:58:31.000Z","msg":"成pack拆開擺入微波爐叮 <br />\n完"},{"pid":"252883e82fea38ca649ae65446ff3b3fda385765","tid":372661,"uid":29464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成pack拆開擺入微波爐叮 <br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60c082fb237b981541228ecda1294b00ec7dc94","tid":372661,"uid":128602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6c28d846589760ada80172e617facec1ccee142b","tid":372661,"uid":8216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成pack拆開擺入微波爐叮 <br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n生叮魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113acd077b7d94b01c461352f46ca3fd3355e440","tid":372661,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"正<br />\n原來咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86eaaa85fb4bc4b390d175996069f3da37af75c9","tid":372661,"uid":28031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/210103_9bafdb7a925970434a9f8781214f7d7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F210103_9bafdb7a925970434a9f8781214f7d7b.jpg&h=f28cd4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此post已完 多謝大家"},{"pid":"4832b8c6a8faa6bb8fe54a9317f27aa9b6e557b5","tid":372661,"uid":29464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/210103_9bafdb7a925970434a9f8781214f7d7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F210103_9bafdb7a925970434a9f8781214f7d7b.jpg&h=f28cd4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此post已完 多謝大家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飯呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee261d7e287cf5e89f38d969b7c58da471e0e59","tid":372661,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:03:17.000Z